{"tid":1407853,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"知唔知新界南總部（荃灣）200米內有咩？","createTime":"2019-08-04T16:06:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T16:59:50.000Z","uid":73617,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c3f0310f10febbb638a75a3dd60ae61a6190b4c0","tid":1407853,"uid":73617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T16:06:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://the-sun.on.cc/cnt/news/20140410/photo/0410-00410-030b6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fthe-sun.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20140410%2Fphoto%2F0410-00410-030b6.jpg&h=12042974&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我知道聽日你班暴徒會入黎荃灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你班人晚晚搞完事都一地磚頭，遮呀垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n扔完垃圾就走，同撞車不顧而去冇分別，我而家話埋比你聽邊到有垃圾站，警告你地唔好亂咁扔垃圾，搞亂我地個荃灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n新界南既各位呀SIR，我向你地致敬呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e36ca62a6b47d95a1e22ea9e63d6b62bb0331f87","tid":1407853,"uid":73617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T16:06:20.000Z","msg":"廢青暴徒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bb04a48644ae069e8a5676289c451687df91783","tid":1407853,"uid":73617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T16:06:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"254ee7c9d570b55eb85173755a0a37dc18aee94d","tid":1407853,"uid":73617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T16:06:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98c242d715c40d3bc791e7236303ed2e21cb9f9b","tid":1407853,"uid":73617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T16:06:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"728f2c1e07dd2dbc81bee22d9c1e61639e99569c","tid":14078